[[bin]]
path = "src/main.rs"
name = "opensearch-filter-proxy"
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
edition = "2024"
required-features = []

[package]
name = "opensearch-filter-proxy"
edition = "2024"
version = "0.0.1"
authors = ["Brehl <gitlab@brehl.dev>"]

[dependencies]
axum = "0.8.4"
envy = "0.4.2"
opensearch = "2.3.0"
serde_json = "1.0.143"
tracing = "0.1.41"

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0"
features = ["derive"]

[dependencies.tokio]
version = "1"
features = ["full"]

[dependencies.tower-http]
version = "0.6.2"
features = ["trace"]

[dependencies.tracing-subscriber]
version = "0.3"
features = ["env-filter"]
